  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "A character who breathes heavy smoke must make a Fortitude save each round (DC 15, +1 per previous check) or spend that round choking and coughing. A character who chokes for 2 consecutive rounds takes 1d6 points of nonlethal damage.\nSmoke obscures vision, giving concealment (20% miss chance) to characters within it.",
